# Build-context ignore for the COMPUTE image (Dockerfile.compute). Unlike the
# repo-root .dockerignore (tuned for the game deploy image, which excludes
# training/ and *.md), this KEEPS training/ + the workspace sources and only
# drops the heavy build/dep artifacts. BuildKit uses <dockerfile>.dockerignore
# when present.
.git/
target/
**/target/
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
**/dist/
**/pkg/
